  <summary date="2023-06-14T10:27:39Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Death Penalty Abolition Act of 2023

This bill prohibits the imposition of a death penalty sentence for a violation of federal law.

It eliminates statutory authority for the death penalty as a sentencing option for federal offenses.

It also requires a person who was sentenced to death before enactment of this bill to be resentenced.</summary>
